name: SYPHON #5
description:
This is Syphon. She is the youngest guardian of works of art that have been discarded by society for being too disruptive for their times. This little girl was born in the metaverse and never ages. Her natural talent is to hack whatever gadgets and systems she wants, and her pumpkin helmet grants the added ability to invade enemies' dreams, as if hacking into their minds.

She just likes numbers and neurons.
